}

{
  "action_id": "2015",
  "action_title": "Prevent pollution from agricultural land or forestry from entering watercourses",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nWe found no studies that evaluated the effects of preventing pollution from agriculture or forestry from entering watercourses on bat populations.\n\n\u2018We found no studies\u2019 means that we have not yet found any studies that have directly evaluated this action during our systematic journal and report searches. Therefore we have been unable to assess whether or not the action is effective or has any harmful impacts. Please get in touch if you know of such a study for this action."
}

